    "text": "We replaced voicemail with Lippy AI, and the difference has been night and day. Calls are answered instantly, messages are actually useful, and customers don’t fall off anymore. It genuinely feels like voicemail finally caught up with how people expect modern businesses to operate.\n\nWhat sold me initially was the quality and tone of the agent. I actually discovered Lippy while trying to get my fingerprints done through a notary, and I was struck by how natural, polished, and human the interaction felt. It wasn’t just “good for AI”—it was impeccable. That’s when I realized this was the exact solution I needed for my company.\n\nI run multiple ventures and wear a lot of hats, so I need systems that can handle complexity: automating inbound calls, qualifying leads, and setting appointments without friction. Lippy delivered on all of that. We were able to build something powerful together, and the impact was immediate.\n\nThis feels less like a tool and more like an extension of the business. I’m genuinely excited about what’s ahead and look forward to a bright collaboration moving forward. 👌🏼",
